.TH MAKEBREAD 1 "February 2026" "makebread 0.3.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
makebread \- a simple bread machine recipe manager
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B makebread
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B makebread
is a comprehensive PySide6/Qt6 application designed for bread machine
enthusiasts who want to organize and manage their bread recipes digitally.
The application provides a user-friendly interface for creating, editing,
and storing bread machine recipes with detailed ingredient lists and
step-by-step instructions.

Key features include importing and exporting recipes in various formats,
pre-configured timer presets optimized for different bread machine models
and brands, intelligent ingredient scaling using baker's percentages to
adjust recipe quantities, and professional recipe card printing for
kitchen reference. The application also supports recipe categorization,
search functionality, and nutritional information tracking to help users
maintain their bread-making workflow efficiently.
.SH OPTIONS
No command-line options. The application launches a graphical interface.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.local/share/makebread/
User data directory containing the recipe database.
